item.title: EP 24 - Why You Little!
item.itunes:title: Why You Little!
item.description:
Today we talk about spiders, gullibility, and the longest running reality show of all time: The Simpsons

Patreon 

https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

The Simpsons is an American classic, and one of my favorite shows. But is it possible that it is not a cartoon but actually a glimpse into the real life nuclear catastrophe that took place in the US during the 80's?

Then we switch gears to some crazy spider "facts" that fooled me until I asked Jeeves.
